Annie Lennox

Pattern of My Life

This single was released on 24 May 2009 in the United Kingdom.

Bleed Red

Polyrically Uncorrect

Mama Don't Get Dressed Up for Nothing

He is a Fellow in Mathematics and Philosophy of Science at Green Templeton College, Oxford University. He is also Pastoral Advisor of Green Templeton College, Oxford, a Fellow of Wycliffe Hall, Oxford and Associate Fellow of the Saïd Business School.

Live in Old Smokey
Live in Old Smokey is a live CD by English singer/songwriter Linda Lewis recorded at Ronnie Scott's in London and issued in 2006.
